If this were a camp like Pit, or Seb King, Juggs, or maybe village (though that's less crucial) maintaining some sort of group balance would certainly be in order.<br>
<br>
People get really caught up in the Warrior rogue enchanter cleric mindset.  I've done Seb Crypt with no crowd control and no evac, I've done crypt without a cleric. I've done guardian wurms and WW dragons with 1-2 melee. I've done howling stones with 2 paladins, a necro, a druid, a rogue, and myself. Hell I've held necro in seb duo with just an epic magician.<br>
<br>
The frenzy camp in velks works like this.<br>
1) Get several melee classes.<br>
1a) if not enough melee, recruit a healer of some sort.<br>
2) pull a or several spider(s)<br>
3) Hit &quot;F8&quot; Key<br>
4) Hit &quot;A&quot; key<br>
5) Repeat 2-5 as needed.<br>
<br>
The only situation in which a group can not hold the camp effectively is if the main healer is a druid, and your only tanks are level 49-54 monks rogues and rangers.  I didn't even have to cast any healing spells last time I was main healer there, I just kept regrowth on the 60 warrior and slowed everything.... no mez, no stuns, and it worked fine. <p><table align="center" border="5" style="border-collapse: collapse; font-family: Arial; color: #8888FF; bordercolor="#9999FF" bordercolorlight="#5555FF" bordercolordark="#000088"><tr><td align="center" bgcolor="#000000" WIDTH="234"><FONT COLOR="#FFFFFF" SIZE=+0><IMG SRC="http://www.grizlorspics.iwarp.com/tunaresuxsmall.jpg"><BR><I>Deny your Maker</i></font></td><td bgcolor="#000000" align="center"><B><FONT COLOR="#5555FF">My Toons:</b><BR><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=45358" target="_blank"><b> </font><FONT COLOR="#CDDFF">Grizlor</a></b></font> Shaman<BR><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=48124" target="_blank"><B><FONT COLOR="#CDDFF">Bigbrawler</a></b></font> Monk<BR><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=56772" target="_blank"><B><FONT COLOR="#CDDFF">Ellone</a></b></font> Rogue<BR><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=177859" target="_blank"><B><FONT COLOR="#CDDFF">Gobobtik</a></b></font> Beastlord<BR><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=152243" target="_blank"><B><FONT COLOR="#CDDFF">Xylophone</a></b></font> Bard</font></td></tr><tr><TD COLSPAN="2" BGCOLOR="#000000"><IMG SRC="http://www.grizlorspics.iwarp.com/quotes/quote1b.gif"></td></tr></table></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#222222><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub43.ezboard.com/uelessarelfstone.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Elessar Elfstone</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_redspot.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle><table style=filter:glow(color=Red strength=4><font color