I find myself repeating myself. If you don't get it now, you most likely never will.<br>
<br>
If and when I am ever leader of the Frenzy camp again, and any of you wanted to be on the list, I would fight for your right to be in the group as hard as I would a friend.<br>
<br>
Now whether Blundor or his guildmates would do the same for me or any other class they deemed &quot;non-essential&quot;, that remains to be seen.<br>
<br>
EDIT: LOL, which reminds me. I even let <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> Linvarwen</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> in the group once despite group members begging me not to. But he had waited for hours and it was his turn. If you must flame, flame me for that. =)<br>
